gh Contrast Cursors\",\"author\":\"Astralock\",\"category\":\"Cursors\",\"downloads\":1839,\"description\":\"Made by Dodger, this mod replaces the game's cursors with larger high contrast cursors, and enlarges character and NPC borders to make them easier to target. You can find the thread at https://forums.homecomingservers.com/topic/8887-wheres-my-cursor/\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=201\u0026file=mods/28/high_contrast_cursors.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/201\"},{\"id\":202,\"name\":\"VFX Visual Improvement Mod\",\"author\":\"Astralock\",\"category\":\"Graphics\",\"downloads\":1811,\"description\":\"Made by Titanman, this mod reduces VFX that blind the screen during team content, especially raids and trials. There's many various VFX changes. See the Homecoming forums thread for details at https://forums.homecomingservers.com/topic/23701-titanman-animation-sprite-ui-texture-mod-tutorial/#comment-285552\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=202\u0026file=mods/28/titanman_vfx.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/202\"},{\"id\":247,\"name\":\"Skin Texture Plus - Female\",\"author\":\"Lumenia\",\"category\":\"Graphics\",\"downloads\":1759,\"description\":\"For comparison: https://forums.homecomingservers.com/topic/51413-alternative-female-skin-textures This is a side project to update the skin textures for female human characters, to add more details and define the parts of the body, without breaking the graphical immersion. The style of choice is more of a \\\"toned\\\" look than heavily muscular like the vanilla skin texture. Currently does not work with the skinless tights due to tights option using a different texture file. I'll add that into the mo\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=247\u0026file=mods/99/SkinTexturePlus_Female.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/247\"},{\"id\":57,\"na