1419,\"description\":\"Original Author: Spctr Removes most, if not all, of Bio Armor's effects (I know there's already min fx for it, but this one also targets the ones without that option. Looking right at you Ablative Carapace.)\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=41\u0026file=mods/0/BioArmorEffectsRemoverv1.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/41\"},{\"id\":40,\"name\":\"Better Super Strength Impact\",\"author\":\"Imported\",\"category\":\"Audio\",\"downloads\":1402,\"description\":\"Original Author: Lithobraker Changes Super Strength impact sounds to have a bit more punch. The comic book \\\"pow!\\\" sound is intact, but I've added an extra \\\"smack\\\" sound, since the originals felt too light to me.\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=40\u0026file=mods/0/BetterSuperStrengthImpact.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/40\"},{\"id\":93,\"name\":\"High Visibility Mouse Cursors Set C\",\"author\":\"Imported\",\"category\":\"Cursors\",\"downloads\":1397,\"description\":\"Original Author: 12thPower Busy screens can make you lose track of your mouse cursor. These cursors should stand out a little more. There are a few variants. If you have requests for different styles, please let me know. I made these back in 2011 and have since lost the original PSD files. Original Source: https://forums.homecomingservers.com/topic/9304-quality-of-life-texture-mods-and-other-things/ Repackaged by Westley Bennett\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=93\u0026file=mods/0/H…105855 tokens truncated…oad_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=308\u0026file=mods/223/NoExcelsion.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/308\"},{\"id\":310,\"name\":\"Disco Bottom Tights\",\"author\":\"Kimmy_Kim\",\"category\":\"Graphics\",\"downloads\":166,\"description\":\"Lowers the top of the Disco Bottom for females to resemble thigh-high stockings and changes the briefs to the same as Bikini 2\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=310\u0026file=mods/922/DiscoBottomStockings.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/310\"},{\"id\":306,\"name\":\"1 Hand Weapon Overhead Smash to Crushing Blow\",\"author\":\"sigr\",\"category\":\"Other\",\"downloads\":158,\"description\":\"Changes the Headsplitter/Cleave/Shatter animation to Titan Weapons/Crushing Blow (fast version).\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=306\u0026file=mods/591/1HWeaponSmashtoCrushingBlow.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/306\"},{\"id\":307,\"name\":\"Cinematic Broadsword\",\"author\":\"RobotRobot\",\"category\":\"Audio\",\"downloads\":143,\"description\":\"A mod that replaces Broadsword SFX with sounds from Mortal Kombat 1. Basically makes Broadsword feel more... swordy. Will unfortunately also affect sets that use the same sounds, like Dual Blades, which doesn't sound as good. :(\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=307\u0026file=mods/878/CinematicBroadsword.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/307\"},{\"id\":296,\"name\":\"Teleport Portal Gun Sounds\",\"author\":\"megaericzero\",\"category\":\"Audio\",\"downloads\":139,\"description\":\"Replaces the loud sound effect of most teleport powers with sounds from the Portal Gun taken from the first Portal game. This affects travel teleports, long-range/zone teleports, and some enemy-teleporting powers. The intent was to make traveling long distances with Teleport easier on the ears without silencing it completely. Enjoy!\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=296\u0026file=mods/205/teleport-portal-gun-sounds.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/296\"},{\"id\":298,\"name\":\"Claws Sound Muffler\",\"author\":\"apache\",\"category\":\"Audio\",\"downloads\":135,\"description\":\"This reduces the sharpness of the claws powerset sounds. It also slightly reduces the volume. Treble and amplification were reduced, while bass was slightly boosted. I found the claws sound effects to be too sharp, much like scratching fingernails on a chalkboard. This mod makes it much easier on the ears.\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=298\u0026file=mods/748/ClawsMuffler.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/298\"},{\"id\":305,\"name\":\"Alternate Animations - Concentrated Strike to Energy Transfer\",\"author\":\"sigr\",\"category\":\"Other\",\"downloads\":132,\"description\":\"Swaps Kinetic Melee's Concentrated Strike animation to Energy Melee's full Energy Transfer animation.\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=305\u0026file=mods/591/ConcentratedStriketoEnergyTransfer.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/305\"},{\"id\":297,\"name\":\"Spin to Typhoon\u0026#039;s Edge\",\"author\":\"sigr\",\"category\":\"Other\",\"downloads\":131,\"description\":\"\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=297\u0026file=mods/591/SpintoTyphoon.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/297\"},{\"id\":316,\"name\":\"Imperial Defense/Blackwing Gloves color re-mask\",\"author\":\"Vanden\",\"category\":\"Graphics\",\"downloads\":112,\"description\":\"Improves the colors on the Imperial Defense and Blackwing gloves. For the Imperial Defense gloves, parts of the gloves with glowing lights (which take Color 2) will now always take Color 1. The armor plates on the fingers now simply take Color 1, instead of being a blend of Color 1 and Color 2. For the Blackwing gloves, adds some extra glowing hexagons, primarily on the Heavy variety so it's not mostly a flat color. Also cleaned up some errant color splotches present on the unmodded color mask. \",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=316\u0026file=mods/751/ImperialDefenseBlackwingGloves.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/316\"},{\"id\":311,\"name\":\"Skunk Tail\",\"author\":\"Kimmy_Kim\",\"category\":\"Graphics\",\"downloads\":109,\"description\":\"Changes the color mask for Ragged Wolf Tail to a striped pattern for skunks\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=311\u0026file=mods/922/SkunkTail.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/311\"},{\"id\":312,\"name\":\"Sonic Melee - Quiet Attune\",\"author\":\"Basilisk\",\"category\":\"Audio\",\"downloads\":98,\"description\":\"Silences the Sonic Melee \\\"Attune\\\" power's activation sound. This leaves the quiet loop, only the loud initial activation is affected.\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=312\u0026file=mods/299/SilenceAttune.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/312\"},{\"id\":314,\"name\":\"Alternate Animations - Storm Kick to Spinning Strike\",\"author\":\"sigr\",\"category\":\"Other\",\"downloads\":95,\"description\":\"Storm Kick -\u003e Martial Assault Spinning Kick Changes the melee AT Storm Kick animation to Spinning Kick/Blaster version of Storm Kick.\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=314\u0026file=mods/591/StormKicktoSpinningKick.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/314\"},{\"id\":313,\"name\":\"Alternate Animations - Storm Punch to Ki Push\",\"author\":\"sigr\",\"category\":\"Other\",\"downloads\":80,\"description\":\"Storm Kick Alt -\u003e Ki Push/Quick Strike Changes the animation from a gut punch to match the Ki Push animation that Blasters get in Martial Combat.\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=313\u0026file=mods/591/StormPunchtoQuickStrike.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/313\"},{\"id\":315,\"name\":\"Alternate Animations - Thunder Kick to Spinning Kick\",\"author\":\"sigr\",\"category\":\"Other\",\"downloads\":80,\"description\":\"Thunder Kick -\u003e Martial Assault Spinning Kick Changes the Thunder Kick animation to a Spinning Kick. Also affects Thunder Kick in Martial Assault.\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=315\u0026file=mods/591/ThunderKicktoSpinningKick.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/315\"},{\"id\":317,\"name\":\"Russian Client Translation\",\"author\":\"Michiyo\",\"category\":\"Languages\",\"downloads\":50,\"description\":\"This is a VERY incomplete translation of the game client to Spanish. This will ONLY EVER translate client strings, nothing from Missions, or NPC Dialog as that text is stored on the server. \\u042d\\u0442\\u043e \\u041e\\u0427\\u0415\\u041d\\u042c \\u043d\\u0435\\u043f\\u043e\\u043b\\u043d\\u044b\\u0439 \\u043f\\u0435\\u0440\\u0435\\u0432\\u043e\\u0434 \\u0438\\u0433\\u0440\\u043e\\u0432\\u043e\\u0433\\u043e \\u043a\\u043b\\u0438\\u0435\\u043d\\u0442\\u0430 \\u043d\\u0430 \\u0440\\u0443\\u0441\\u0441\\u043a\\u0438\\u0439 \\u044f\\u0437\\u044b\\u043a. \\u041f\\u0435\\u0440\\u0435\\u0432\\u043e\\u0434\\u044f\\u0442\\u0441\\u044f \\u0422\\u041e\\u041b\\u042c\\u041a\\u041e \\u0441\\u0442\\u0440\\u043e\\u043a\\u0438 \\u043a\\u043b\\u0438\\u0435\\u043d\\u0442\\u0430 \\u2014 \\u0442\\u0435\\u043a\\u0441\\u0442\\u044b \\u043c\\u0438\\u0441\\u0441\\u0438\\u0439 \\u0438 \\u0434\\u0438\\u0430\\u043b\\u043e\\u0433\\u0438 NPC \\u043d\\u0435 \\u0437\\u0430\\u0442\\u0440\\u0430\\u0433\\u0438\\u0432\\u0430\\u044e\\u0442\\u0441\\u044f, \\u0442\\u0430\\u043a \\u043a\\u0430\\u043a \\u043e\\u043d\\u0438 \\u0445\\u0440\\u0430\\u043d\\u044f\\u0442\\u0441\\u044f \\u043d\\u0430 \\u0441\\u0435\\u0440\\u0432\\u0435\\u0440\\u0435.\",\"download_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods//mods/download.php?id=317\u0026file=mods/17/RussianClient.pigg\",\"page_url\":\"https://cityofheroes.dev/mods/mod/317\"},{\"id\":318,\"name\":\"Alternate Animations - Hand Clap to Ground Punch\",\"author\":\